<p>
<url href="https://sites.google.com/view/stevebutler">Dr. Steve Butler</url> is a professor and the Barbara J. Janson Professor in the Department of Mathematics at Iowa State University. Prior to coming to Iowa State he did a three year NSF PostDoc under the supervision of Benny Sudakov at UCLA.  Before that he earned his doctorate degree in mathematics at UC San Diego under the supervision of Fan Chung. In addition Dr. Butler worked extensively with Ron Graham.
